          "INC-SOURCE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The 8Li beam was produced by using the EXCYT facility",
                "at INFN-LNS, Catania. The EXCYT production-acceleration",
                "system uses the ISOL technique. It is based on a K-800",
                "superconducting cyclotron, as a driver for stable heavy",
                "ion beams and on a 15 MV tandem for post-accelerating",
                "the radioactive ion beams produced in a target-ion",
                "source (TIS) assembly.",
                "The production of the radioactive ions was performed by",
                "injecting a 13C4+ primary beam of 45 MeV/amu on a",
                "graphite target up to a beam power of 150 W."
              ]
            }
          ],
